				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I would also recommend alchemist, it is the easiest to level, it uses a wide range of resources so it is very easy to harvest, and frankly you make alot of money quickly.  If I wanted to work hard enough to keep up with demand I would gain a level or two a day easy.  However you need to watch your servers to see what types of tradeskillers you have it is very easy to find a certian trade overpopulated (oddly I see quite alot of provisioners now).
<br />

<br />
Sages are one of the hardest and most expensive to level up, it takes alot of time and dedication and I would even suggest a seperate account for constant selling.  As far as I know very few servers have level 50 sages.<br />_________________<br />______________________
<br />

